            safety. As such, regular updates to these will be made available through the Microsoft
            Health CUI Website.
        </p>
        <p>
            For all future releases, the controls will be developed in <a target="_blank" href="http://windowsclient.net/WPF/"
                title="Link to Windows Presentation Foundation page on WindowsClient.NET (New Window)">
